{"word":"G4095 - πίνω - pínō - pee'-no - Drink","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pee'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Drink</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குடி, பானம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to drink"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>The first is a prolonged form of the second, which (together with the third form) occurs only as an alternate in certain tenses; to <i>imbibe</i> (literally or figuratively): - drink.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2666/2666\">G2666</a>, <a href=\"#/G4095/4095\">G4095</a>, <a href=\"#/G4188/4188\">G4188</a>, <a href=\"#/G4213/4213\">G4213</a>, <a href=\"#/G4221/4221\">G4221</a>, <a href=\"#/G4222/4222\">G4222</a>, <a href=\"#/G4224/4224\">G4224</a>"}]}